    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Regenerate</strong> (Level 7 Transmutation)</p><p>You touch a creature and stimulate its natural healing ability. The target regains 4d8 + 15 hit points. For the duration of the spell, the target regains 1 hit point at the start of each of its turns (10 hit points each minute).</p><p>The target's severed body members (fingers, legs, tails, and so on), if any, are restored after 2 minutes. If you have the severed part and hold it to the stump, the spell instantaneously causes the limb to knit to the stump.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A prayer wheel and holy water.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 minute | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> 1 hour</p><p><em>Classes: Bard, Cleric, Druid</em></p>",
